{"type":"message","id":"1a4ffff5","parentId":"c56d6452","timestamp":"2026-03-21T03:59:26.300Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_jn2sizb8f8g1h2ayrsmza9zv","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1.[单选]浮来山风景区内最著名的景观是什么？\nA. 青灰色的石灰岩山体\nB. 四千多年的银杏古树\nC. 定林寺的飞檐斗拱\nD. 朝阳观的摩崖造像\n答案：B\n解析：根据原文描述，浮来山风景区\"因'天下银杏第一树'而名扬四海——树龄逾四千年的银杏古树巍然矗立于定林寺前\"，这是景区最著名的景观。其他选项虽然也是景区内的重要景点，但不是最著名的。\n题目难度：易"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774065566296}}
{"type":"message","id":"d9d5037a","parentId":"1a4ffff5","timestamp":"2026-03-21T03:59:28.684Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哦，只生成了一道题目？让我检查一下，我们要求每个题型一道，总共 6 道题，让我重新运行：\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5ie0tcsp1v3sqyi1gtaom008","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator && rm output_浮来山.md && /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/venv/bin/python scripts/generate_quiz.py --input content.txt --count 6 --types single,multiple,uncertain,judgment,fill,short --provider zhipu --output output_浮来山.md","timeout":180}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1502,"output":170,"cacheRead":25400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27072,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774065566303}}
