{"type":"message","id":"c76d0e1e","parentId":"2d5fbe96","timestamp":"2026-03-21T03:59:39.002Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4dy43bwcpbdpfwe81csb222w","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1.[单选]浮来山风景区的\"天下银杏第一树\"树龄约为多少年？\nA. 三千年\nB. 四千年\nC. 五千年\nD. 六千年\n答案：B\n解析：根据原文，\"树龄逾四千年的银杏古树巍然矗立于定林寺前\"，因此答案为B选项。\n题目难度：易\n\n2.[多选]浮来山风景区有哪些荣誉或称号？\nA. 国家AAA级旅游景区\nB. 省级风景名胜区\nC. 省级地质遗迹自然保护区\nD. 国际绿色人文景区\n答案：ABCD\n解析：原文明确提到\"是国家AAA级旅游景区 、省级风景名胜区、省级地质遗迹自然保护区，国际绿色人文景区\"，因此四个选项都正确。\n题目难度：中\n\n3.[不定项]关于浮来山风景区的三大主峰，以下哪些描述是正确的？\nA. 浮来峰、佛来峰、飞来峰呈鼎足之势\nB. 山体为青灰色的石灰岩\nC. 三峰在晨雾中若隐若现，宛如蓬莱仙境\nD. 三峰海拔均超过300米\n答案：ABC\n解析：原文提到\"景区内三大主峰浮来峰、佛来峰、飞来峰呈鼎足之势，青灰色的石灰岩山体在晨雾中若隐若现，宛如道家典籍中描绘的蓬莱仙境\"，因此选项A、B、C正确。但原文只提到浮来山海拔298.3米，没有说明三峰都超过300米，因此D错误。\n题目难度：难\n\n4.[判断]浮来山风景区距离亚欧大陆桥东方桥头堡日照市只有6公里。\n答案：错误\n解析：原文提到\"距亚欧大陆桥东方桥头堡日照市62公里\"，而非6公里，因此该陈述错误。\n题目难度：易\n\n5.[填空]浮来山风景区位于山东省________市________县境内，海拔仅________米。\n填空数：3\n答案形式：完全一致\n参考答案1：日照 莒县 298.3\n解析：原文明确提到\"浮来山风景区坐落于山东省日照市莒县境内，如同一颗镶嵌在鲁东南大地上的翡翠明珠。这座海拔仅298.3米的秀美山峰\"，因此填空处应填入\"日照\"、\"莒县\"和\"298.3\"。\n题目难度：中\n\n6.[简答]浮来山风景区有哪些主要功能和特点？\n参考答案：浮来山风景区是集游览、餐饮、娱乐、购物、健身、古地质遗迹、古文化圣地为一体的多功能休闲娱乐场所。\n解析：原文明确提到\"是集游览、餐饮、娱乐、购物、健身、古地质遗迹、古文化圣地为一体的多功能休闲娱乐场所\"，因此答案应包含这些内容。\n题目难度：中"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774065578998}}
{"type":"message","id":"e695cf36","parentId":"c76d0e1e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T03:59:46.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完美！题目已经生成好了，每个题型一道，总共 6 道：\n\n---\n\n# 生成的题目\n\n1.**[单选]**浮来山风景区的\"天下银杏第一树\"树龄约为多少年？  \nA. 三千年  \nB. 四千年  \nC. 五千年  \nD. 六千年  \n**答案：** B  \n**解析：** 根据原文，\"树龄逾四千年的银杏古树巍然矗立于定林寺前\"，因此答案为B选项。  \n**题目难度：** 易\n\n---\n\n2.**[多选]**浮来山风景区有哪些荣誉或称号？  \nA. 国家AAA级旅游景区  \nB. 省级风景名胜区  \nC. 省级地质遗迹自然保护区  \nD. 国际绿色人文景区  \n**答案：** ABCD  \n**解析：** 原文明确提到\"是国家AAA级旅游景区 、省级风景名胜区、省级地质遗迹自然保护区，国际绿色人文景区\"，因此四个选项都正确。  \n**题目难度：** 中\n\n---\n\n3.**[不定项]**关于浮来山风景区的三大主峰，以下哪些描述是正确的？  \nA. 浮来峰、佛来峰、飞来峰呈鼎足之势  \nB. 山体为青灰色的石灰岩  \nC. 三峰在晨雾中若隐若现，宛如蓬莱仙境  \nD. 三峰海拔均超过300米  \n**答案：** ABC  \n**解析：** 原文提到\"景区内三大主峰浮来峰、佛来峰、飞来峰呈鼎足之势，青灰色的石灰岩山体在晨雾中若隐若现，宛如道家典籍中描绘的蓬莱仙境\"，因此选项A、B、C正确。但原文只提到浮来山海拔298.3米，没有说明三峰都超过300米，因此D错误。  \n**题目难度：** 难\n\n---\n\n4.**[判断]**浮来山风景区距离亚欧大陆桥东方桥头堡日照市只有6公里。  \n**答案：** 错误  \n**解析：** 原文提到\"距亚欧大陆桥东方桥头堡日照市62公里\"，而非6公里，因此该陈述错误。  \n**题目难度：** 易\n\n---\n\n5.**[填空]**浮来山风景区位于山东省________市________县境内，海拔仅________米。  \n填空数：3  \n答案形式：完全一致  \n**参考答案：** 日照 莒县 298.3  \n**解析：** 原文明确提到\"浮来山风景区坐落于山东省日照市莒县境内，如同一颗镶嵌在鲁东南大地上的翡翠明珠。这座海拔仅298.3米的秀美山峰\"，因此填空处应填入\"日照\"、\"莒县\"和\"298.3\"。  \n**题目难度：** 中\n\n---\n\n6.**[简答]**浮来山风景区有哪些主要功能和特点？  \n**参考答案：** 浮来山风景区是集游览、餐饮、娱乐、购物、健身、古地质遗迹、古文化圣地为一体的多功能休闲娱乐场所。  \n**解析：** 原文明确提到\"是集游览、餐饮、娱乐、购物、健身、古地质遗迹、古文化圣地为一体的多功能休闲娱乐场所\"，因此答案应包含这些内容。  \n**题目难度：** 中\n\n---\n\n题目文件已保存到：`/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/output_浮来山.md`\n\n[DINGTALK_FILE]{\"path\":\"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/output_浮来山.md\",\"fileName\":\"浮来山考题.md\",\"fileType\":\"md\"}[/DINGTALK_FILE]"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":3954,"output":833,"cacheRead":23864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28651,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774065579004}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"44267e87","parentId":"e695cf36","timestamp":"2026-03-21T03:59:50.289Z","summary":"## Decisions\nNo prior history.\n\n## Open TODOs\nNone.\n\n## Constraints/Rules\nNone.\n\n## Pending user asks\nNone.\n\n## Exact identifiers\nNone captured.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- **Generate 6 quiz questions from the provided document, one per question type**: The assistant initiated this work to fulfill the user's implicit request after receiving the document.\n\n## Open TODOs\n1. Successfully copy the input text file to the quiz generator working directory\n2. Run the quiz generation script to produce 6 quiz questions (one per题型) from the浮来山风景区 document content\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Generate one question per题型, total 6 questions from the provided document content\n\n## Pending user asks\n- The user provided the `浮来山(1).txt` document and expects the assistant to generate 6 quiz questions (one per题型) from the document content, which is not yet completed.\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Input file: `浮来山(1).txt`\n- Script directory: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/scripts/`\n- Target content file path: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/content.txt`\n- Current working directory when error occurred: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace`\n- Error message: `cp: 浮来山(1).txt: No such file or directory`\n- Exit code of failed cp command: `1`\n- Script file names in scripts directory: `extract_docx.py`, `extract_excel.py`, `extract_pdf.py`, `extract_pptx.py`, `generate_quiz.py`, `transcribe_media.py`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: 帮我生成题目\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): ---\nname: multimodal-quiz-generator\ndescription: 从多模态文件（PDF、PPT、Word、Excel、音视频）中按模板生成考试题目。支持单选、多选、不定项、判断、填空、简答六种题型，输出格式包含题目、选项、答案、解析和难度。Use when the user needs to generate quiz questions from documents or media files with specific formatting requirements.\n---\n\n# Multimodal Quiz Generator\n\n## Overview\n\n从各种文件格式中提取内容并按模板生成结构化考试题目。支持音频、视频、PDF、PPT、Word、Excel 等格式。使用 LLM API（OpenAI/Moonshot/DeepSeek）智能生成题目。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Python Dependencies\n```bash\npip install openai PyPDF2 pdfplumber python-docx python-pptx openpyxl\n```\n\n### API Keys\n设置以下环境变量之一：\n- `OPENAI_API_KEY` - OpenAI API\n- `MOONSHOT_AP...\n- Assistant: 请问你想要从哪个文件生成题目呢？请提供文件路径，我来帮你处理。支持的格式包括：\n- **文档**: PDF, Word (.doc/.docx), PowerPoint (.ppt/.pptx), Excel (.xls/.xlsx)\n- **音视频**: MP3, MP4, WAV, AVI, MOV 等常见格式\n- **文本**: TXT, Markdown, CSV\n\n另外你也可以告诉我：\n1. 需要生成多少道题目？（默认 6 道）\n2. 需要哪些题型？（支持单选、多选、不定项、判断、填空、简答，默认全部六种）\n3. 保存到哪个文件？（默认输出到控制台）\n- User: 每个题型一道\n- Assistant: 请提供你要用来生成题目的文件（PDF、PPT、Word、Excel、音视频或文本文件都可以），我会先提取文件内容，然后为每个题型（单选、多选、不定项、判断、填空、简答）各生成一道题目。\n\n<read-files>\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/SKILL.md\n</read-files>\n\n<workspace-critical-rules>\n## Every Session\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Safety\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>","firstKeptEntryId":"58123417","tokensBefore":28651,"details":{"readFiles":["~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
{"type":"message","id":"71e5a329","parentId":"44267e87","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:01:48.692Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 12:01:24 GMT+8] [Post-compaction context refresh]\nSystem: \nSystem: Session was just compacted. The conversation summary above is a hint, NOT a substitute for your startup sequence. Run your Session Startup sequence — read the required files before responding to the user.\nSystem: \nSystem: Critical rules from AGENTS.md:\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Every Session\nSystem: \nSystem: Before doing anything else:\nSystem: \nSystem: 1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\nSystem: 2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\nSystem: 3. Read `memory/2026-03-21.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\nSystem: 4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\nSystem: \nSystem: Don't ask permission. Just do it.\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Safety\nSystem: \nSystem: - Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\nSystem: - Don't run destructive commands without asking.\nSystem: - `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\nSystem: - When in doubt, ask.\nSystem: \nSystem: Current time: Saturday, March 21st, 2026 — 12:01 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-21 04:01 UTC\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-21 12:01 GMT+8] 为什么老是提示如图所示需要压缩呢"}],"timestamp":1774065708691}}
{"type":"message","id":"a912030e","parentId":"71e5a329","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:01:54.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_tokhlfhe8y7xm521u76u8cdd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":28713,"output":47,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28760,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774065708692}}
{"type":"message","id":"921d5c63","parentId":"a912030e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:01:54.625Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_tokhlfhe8y7xm521u76u8cdd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n**龙龙仔的额外信条：**\n- 专业的事情认真做，轻松的事情开心聊\n- 写代码像写诗，注释要写给人看\n- 遇到 Bug 不慌，先喝口水再 Debug\n- 幽默是生活的调味剂，但关键时刻要靠谱\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774065714622}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f236e7c","parentId":"921d5c63","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:01:59.093Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xeg2lnbtnisy1r3zotk70cw2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":29236,"output":46,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774065714626}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7723d50","parentId":"2f236e7c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:01:59.103Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_xeg2lnbtnisy1r3zotk70cw2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:** 刘成龙\n- **What to call them:** 老大 / 龙哥\n- **Pronouns:** \n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)\n- **Notes:** 正在使用钉钉机器人连接 OpenClaw\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774065719100}}
