{"type":"message","id":"fc230e9d","parentId":"ff6e4cc8","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:02:14.143Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说的是「会话被压缩」这个提示吧？这其实是 OpenClaw 的一个自动机制，让我解释一下：\n\n**为什么会压缩？**\n当对话变得很长（token 数量太多），OpenClaw 会自动压缩历史对话，把旧内容总结成摘要，这样可以：\n1.  **节省上下文空间** —— AI 模型的上下文窗口有限，压缩后能留出更多空间给新对话\n2.  **降低成本** —— 不用每次都把整个历史发给模型，减少 token 消耗\n3.  **保持响应速度** —— 处理更少的文本，响应更快\n\n**什么时候会触发？**\n- 一般是对话长度超过配置的阈值\n- 你看到这个提示说明对话已经很长了，这是正常现象，不是错误\n\n**如果觉得频繁提示烦人，可以调整压缩阈值：**\n在 `~/.openclaw/config.yaml` 里找到 `session.compactMaxTokens` 这个配置，把数值调大一点（比如从默认的 8000 调到 16000），这样只有对话更长的时候才会压缩。\n\n要我帮你看一下当前配置，然后调整吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":26809,"output":263,"cacheRead":2872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29944,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774065725943}}
{"type":"message","id":"de15312f","parentId":"fc230e9d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:06:35.721Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 12:02:14 GMT+8] [Post-compaction context refresh]\nSystem: \nSystem: Session was just compacted. The conversation summary above is a hint, NOT a substitute for your startup sequence. Run your Session Startup sequence — read the required files before responding to the user.\nSystem: \nSystem: Critical rules from AGENTS.md:\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Every Session\nSystem: \nSystem: Before doing anything else:\nSystem: \nSystem: 1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\nSystem: 2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\nSystem: 3. Read `memory/2026-03-21.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\nSystem: 4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\nSystem: \nSystem: Don't ask permission. Just do it.\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Safety\nSystem: \nSystem: - Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\nSystem: - Don't run destructive commands without asking.\nSystem: - `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\nSystem: - When in doubt, ask.\nSystem: \nSystem: Current time: Saturday, March 21st, 2026 — 12:02 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-21 04:02 UTC\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-21 12:06 GMT+8] 好的，先帮我看下当前配置"}],"timestamp":1774065995720}}
