{"type":"message","id":"e0e6c02d","parentId":"d686c65b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:06:43.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根据当前配置，问题出在这里：\n\n```json\n\"compaction\": {\n  \"maxInputTokens\": 15000,\n  \"targetTokens\": 8000\n}\n```\n\n你的配置中设置了输入超过 **15000 tokens** 就触发压缩，目标压缩到 **8000 tokens**。但因为钉钉消息本身就比较多，每次对话后 token 增长很快，所以很快就到阈值了，导致频繁压缩。\n\n建议调整这个阈值，让它更大一些：\n\n```json\n\"compaction\": {\n  \"maxInputTokens\": 50000,\n  \"targetTokens\": 30000\n}\n```\n\n需要我帮你修改这个配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":22086,"output":166,"cacheRead":4408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26660,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774065998685}}
{"type":"message","id":"470d3951","parentId":"e0e6c02d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:09:44.211Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 12:06:43 GMT+8] [Post-compaction context refresh]\nSystem: \nSystem: Session was just compacted. The conversation summary above is a hint, NOT a substitute for your startup sequence. Run your Session Startup sequence — read the required files before responding to the user.\nSystem: \nSystem: Critical rules from AGENTS.md:\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Every Session\nSystem: \nSystem: Before doing anything else:\nSystem: \nSystem: 1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\nSystem: 2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\nSystem: 3. Read `memory/2026-03-21.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\nSystem: 4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\nSystem: \nSystem: Don't ask permission. Just do it.\nSystem: \nSystem: ## Safety\nSystem: \nSystem: - Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\nSystem: - Don't run destructive commands without asking.\nSystem: - `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\nSystem: - When in doubt, ask.\nSystem: \nSystem: Current time: Saturday, March 21st, 2026 — 12:06 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-21 04:06 UTC\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-21 12:09 GMT+8] 问题是我刚刚开始聊天呢，为什么一开始就那么多token"}],"timestamp":1774066184209}}
