{"type":"message","id":"0949a928","parentId":"bd080282","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:10:00.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！你现在用的默认模型 `ark-code-latest` 的上下文窗口只设置了 **16000 token**，而且 `maxTokens` 只有 **4096**。**但关键问题不在这里 ——**\n\n你刚刚说\"刚一开始聊天\"就提示压缩，我看看 `session.compactMaxTokens` 的配置：**它根本就没配置，用的是默认值！**\n\n默认的 `compactMaxTokens` 一般是 8000，而你的模型上下文总共才 16000，所以刚聊几句就触发压缩了。\n\n让我帮你加上这个配置，把压缩阈值提高到 12000（留出空间给模型响应）：\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0f5xvt4o1v7qqiyn133x9bhx","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","patch":{"session":{"compactMaxTokens":12000}},"note":"增加会话压缩阈值，从默认的 8000 改为 12000，减少频繁压缩提示"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":4189,"output":258,"cacheRead":26936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774066195434}}
