{"type":"message","id":"97cf6c55","parentId":"f953dbce","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:19:03.396Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，已经恢复到修改前的状态了。现在让我重新看一下，压缩相关的正确配置位置是在 `agents.defaults.compaction`：\n\n现在你的配置里只有：\n```json\n\"compaction\": {\n  \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n}\n```\n\n真正控制压缩阈值的参数是 `maxInputTokens` 和 `targetTokens`，它们都应该放在 `agents.defaults.compaction` 下面。你之前看到的配置截图显示压缩阈值就是 `maxInputTokens: 15000`，但这个参数现在在你的配置里不存在，所以用的默认值可能更小。\n\n让我看看当前配置里 `compaction` 在哪里，我给你指出来：\n\n```\n位置就在：agents → defaults → compaction\n\n你现在是：\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      // ...\n      \"compaction\": {\n        \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n      },\n      // ...\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n需要改成：\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      // ...\n      \"compaction\": {\n        \"mode\": \"safeguard\",\n        \"maxInputTokens\": 50000,\n        \"targetTokens\": 30000\n      },\n      // ...\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n你看，这样才对。我刚才改错地方了，把 `session` 放到最外层是不对的。正确的位置是 `agents.defaults.compaction` 下面加那两个参数。\n\n需要我帮你改吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":648,"output":363,"cacheRead":32568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33579,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774066739296}}
