{"type":"message","id":"92f20a30","parentId":"a3247dd5","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:20:32.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"原来配置已经加上 `session.compactMaxTokens: 12000` 了！但问题出在另外一个地方：\n\n你看这个结构：\n```json\n\"session\": {\n  \"compactMaxTokens\": 12000\n},\n\"agents\": {\n  \"defaults\": {\n    // ... 这里已经有个 compaction 配置了！\n    \"compaction\": {\n      \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n    },\n```\n\n现在发现了，OpenClaw 的压缩配置其实分两级：\n1.  **根级别 `session.compactMaxTokens`** —— 这是全局设置\n2.  **agents.defaults.compaction** —— 这是默认 Agent 的压缩设置，里面也可以有 `maxInputTokens` 和 `targetTokens`\n\n你当前 agent 配置有 `compaction`，所以它用的是 agents 级别的配置，里面没有显式设置 `maxInputTokens`，会用默认的 15000，而你的模型上下文只有 16000。所以一聊天就触发了。\n\n让我把 `maxInputTokens` 和 `targetTokens` 放到正确的位置：\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_hw57wq2p35muxv1jkwffw3rc","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak","old_string":"  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com/ark-code-latest\"\n      },\n      \"models\": {\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\": {\n          \"alias\": \"Kimi\"\n        },\n        \"zhipu/glm-4-flash\": {\n          \"alias\": \"GLM-Flash\"\n        },\n        \"zhipu/glm-4-plus\": {\n          \"alias\": \"GLM-Plus\"\n        },\n        \"ollama/qwen3:8b\": {\n          \"alias\": \"Qwen3-8B\"\n        },\n        \"custom-127-0-0-1-11434/qwen3:8b\": {},\n        \"custom-127-0-0-1-11434/qwen3.5:4b\": {},\n        \"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com/ark-code-latest\": {}\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace\",\n      \"compaction\": {\n        \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n      },","new_string":"  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com/ark-code-latest\"\n      },\n      \"models\": {\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\": {\n          \"alias\": \"Kimi\"\n        },\n        \"zhipu/glm-4-flash\": {\n          \"alias\": \"GLM-Flash\"\n        },\n        \"zhipu/glm-4-plus\": {\n          \"alias\": \"GLM-Plus\"\n        },\n        \"ollama/qwen3:8b\": {\n          \"alias\": \"Qwen3-8B\"\n        },\n        \"custom-127-0-0-1-11434/qwen3:8b\": {},\n        \"custom-127-0-0-1-11434/qwen3.5:4b\": {},\n        \"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com/ark-code-latest\": {}\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace\",\n      \"compaction\": {\n        \"mode\": \"safeguard\",\n        \"maxInputTokens\": 12000,\n        \"targetTokens\": 8000\n      },"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":32189,"output":927,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33116,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774066821954}}
