{"type":"message","id":"f5b3d759","parentId":"1995aa4e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:20:41.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好啦！已经改对地方了。\n\n让我解释一下：\n\n**原来的问题：**\n- 你当前模型 `ark-code-latest` 的上下文窗口只有 **16000 token**\n- 而 `agents.defaults.compaction` 里面没有配置 `maxInputTokens`，用的默认值 **15000**\n- 所以只要对话一超过 15000 token 就压缩 —— 但这离上下文窗口只剩 1000 token 了，所以一聊天就触发压缩\n\n**正确的修改：**\n✅ 我已经在 **`agents.defaults.compaction`** 这个正确位置加上了：\n```json\n\"compaction\": {\n  \"mode\": \"safeguard\",\n  \"maxInputTokens\": 12000,\n  \"targetTokens\": 8000\n}\n```\n\n这样：\n- 对话到 **12000 token** 才会触发压缩（你的模型总共 16000，留出 4000 给输出）\n- 压缩后目标是 **8000 token**，还有充足空间继续聊\n\n现在重启 OpenClaw 让配置生效：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5ve3itjqvy782nicip9hrqvd","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"restart","note":"修复了压缩配置位置，在正确的 compaction 块设置了 maxInputTokens: 12000","delayMs":1000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":28820,"output":359,"cacheRead":4408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33587,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774066834360}}
{"type":"message","id":"26138c3b","parentId":"f5b3d759","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:20:41.957Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5ve3itjqvy782nicip9hrqvd","toolName":"gateway","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"ok\": true,\n  \"pid\": 28528,\n  \"signal\": \"SIGUSR1\",\n  \"delayMs\": 1000,\n  \"mode\": \"emit\",\n  \"coalesced\": false,\n  \"cooldownMsApplied\": 0\n}"}],"details":{"ok":true,"pid":28528,"signal":"SIGUSR1","delayMs":1000,"mode":"emit","coalesced":false,"cooldownMsApplied":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774066841955}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ad09730","parentId":"26138c3b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:20:46.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定了！这次位置改对了 ✅\n\n**总结一下修改：**\n\n- 压缩阈值应该放在 `agents.defaults.compaction` 里面，而不是放在根 `session` 下\n- 现在配置：\n  - `maxInputTokens`: **12000** → 超过这个长度才压缩\n  - `targetTokens`: **8000** → 压缩到这个目标长度\n\n因为你的模型上下文窗口总共只有 16000，压缩到 8000 后还能留出 8000 给后续对话，应该不会一上来就提示压缩了。如果还是觉得频繁，还可以再把 `maxInputTokens` 调到 13000 或 14000。\n\n现在重启完成了，你再试试聊天吧，应该正常了 😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":589,"output":185,"cacheRead":33080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33854,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774066841959}}
